faces.description: Michael Yo is an American actor, stand-up comedian and television host who co-hosts The Insider on CBS, as well as Yo Show on Yahoo! TV. Yo also appears regularly on the comedy panel of E!'s Chelsea Lately, as a guest host for The Talk on CBS, and as pop-culture commentator on HLN's Showbiz Tonight.
